151
00:07:46,176 --> 00:07:51,140
Stereotypes are what allow us to efficiently navigate our world, to deal with the onslaught

152
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:54,843
of information that is always being fired at us at any given moment, especially in today's

153
00:07:54,903 --> 00:07:55,483
modern time.

154
00:07:57,045 --> 00:08:01,388
Unfortunately, it means we suck when it comes to random at small scales, because we're so

155
00:08:01,849 --> 00:08:06,333
intense, intensely bound to finding a pattern, that we will find it in even the smallest

156
00:08:06,393 --> 00:08:06,533
thing.

