169
00:08:37,095 --> 00:08:38,796
And that includes visuals and all sorts of things.

170
00:08:39,967 --> 00:08:42,148
And that's because things stand out if they don't fit.

171
00:08:42,968 --> 00:08:47,690
Our entire brains really are giant pattern matching systems,

172
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:50,811
